## 5. TEST CASE SPECIFICATION

For each test case, define:

```json
{
  "id": "tc-01",
  "name": "Short descriptive name",
  "description": "What this test verifies",
  "type": "unit|integration|e2e",
  "target": "src/module.py::function_name",
  "inputs": "Description of test inputs",
  "expected_result": "What should happen",
  "priority": "critical|high|medium|low",
  "status": "pending"
}
```

---

## 6. OUTPUT FORMAT

### File 1: `artifacts/07-test-plan.md`
Human-readable test plan document.

### File 2: `artifacts/08-test-plan.json`
Machine-readable test plan JSON:
```json
{
  "test_plan_version": 1,
  "generated_phase": "{{ phase }}",
  "cycle": {{ cycle }},
  "total_tests": N,
  "by_type": {"unit": N, "integration": N, "e2e": N},
  "test_cases": [...]
}
```

